dc_title_s: PSAP Service Area Boundaries Dane County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data layer represents 911 Public Safety Answering Point (PSAP) service area boundaries in Dane County, Wisconsin in 2019. According to the National Emergency Number Association (NENA), a Public Safety Answering Point (PSAP) is a facility equipped and staffed to receive 9-1-1 calls. The service area is the geographic area within which a 911 call placed using a landline is answered at the associated PSAP.
